---
description: Content rules for Shower presentation writing
globs: **/*.html, content/**/*
---

- One idea per slide.
- Prefer short bullets over long paragraphs.
- Use `.next` for staged reveals.
- For every `ul.deck-list`, use `li.icon` and set explicit `data-icon` on each list item unless user asks otherwise.
- Avoid more than 6 bullets per slide.
- Write concise, presentation-friendly Russian copy by default.
